{"tid":491071,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"十個cosplay十一個係雞的進化史！！！","createTime":"2017-12-06T07:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T04:52:43.000Z","uid":78533,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"019f44932f5eef00cc51fb401c5bd865025bdc91","tid":491071,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚明  眼見好多人玩cosplay頭幾個月都正正常常 之後又慢慢就會進化做雞變做雞！<br />\n<br />\n進化過程大約係咁<br />\n1.開始玩cosplay <br />\n2.買衫<br />\n3.出去影相 post Facebook <br />\n4.同人講係為興趣<br />\n5.有樣既開始有人氣<br />\n6.開專頁<br />\n7.改奇怪網名<br />\n8.開始自己改裝下道具<br />\n9.又要出去影下相 開始識下其他玩cosplay既人<br />\n10.比人叫去一齊影相（例如雷拉母雞）<br />\n11.開始post果次既私影相（分幾次post)<br />\n12.share角色相 問大家想佢cos咩<br />\n13.share人地cos得靚影得靚既相話想啪<br />\n14.睇下淫賤攝影龍友留言話pm u<br />\n15.開始有收入 <br />\n16.啪啪下又想啪下d少女情懷系列 又咩私之攝影<br />\n17.跟手人氣越黎越多 開下台 吹下水<br />\n18.開始問 大家想唔想睇cos死水庫既xx角色 <br />\n19.貼張遮樣相<br />\n20.狗公數量瘋狂上升<br />\n21.開始瘋狂啪攝私影<br />\n22.吹下自己努力搵錢玩cos好辛苦 大家多多支持<br />\n23.開始賣2衫褲鞋襪（絲襪）<br />\n24.差唔多又絕對領域日 又要貼下腳圖<br />\n25.狗公數再上升<br />\n26.無聊去做下女僕<br />\n27"},{"pid":"bb3e35bd74204dfdc0da1e30ed8ec764420ab9bd","tid":491071,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打到累 唔撚打了"},{"pid":"926ca6293cf5a9d21ce4ba3b5801e577017f8ab5","tid":491071,"uid":106018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"有無毒撚cosplay進化史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a4728fbbcfed71b200607b133086f4ebf13856","tid":491071,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"28ca985b2361046ddbf823bee3c471707425785c","tid":491071,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:23:06.000Z","msg":"27.跟手share呢個post屌柒樓主 以示自己清白"},{"pid":"98e4a8b643a1ff2d479ee6372868eb943244c8a5","tid":491071,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef54b60599c74f8624bbed11ddc06fa3d6f77747","tid":491071,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無毒撚cosplay進化史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚去到5 就會因為無人氣 因為純為興趣 咁玩<br />\n 6.出下活動<br />\n7.見到有人影合照又狗衝去一齊影<br />\n8.番到屋企上fb搵番今日其他cosplay 既相 睇下有冇自己<br />\n9.偷圖貼係自己fb話好開心 今日好有氣氛<br />\n56789<br />\n56789<br />\n56789<br />\n56789"},{"pid":"11f785e85d9989eaa786fbf07c4f03c02938846d","tid":491071,"uid":78533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Can't agger more<br />\n雞都算係職業，識收錢<br />\nCoser根本雞都不如！係公廁！係肉便器！</blockquote><br />\n班雞影相緊係有錢收啦！不過可能唔多 所以要去做下女僕<br />\n<br />\n唔會冇錢都比人係咁影掛"},{"pid":"606a24c3a045710835babad93c76ac6886087a7a","tid":491071,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"7306327da724e5e71a81c3ec42ac664da8473326","tid":491071,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606a24c3a045710835babad93c76ac6886087a7a","tid":491071,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事實邊有得駁"},{"pid":"4232732e81679631c173bfcd4ab9a3f26d8660ab","tid":491071,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7306327da724e5e71a81c3ec42ac664da8473326","tid":491071,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606a24c3a045710835babad93c76ac6886087a7a","tid":491071,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201